By submitting your work to this contest, you allow the Stanford Story Slam and [TODO] to publish your work at least: once in print, and once online. The collaborating authors will be given full credit. Besides this, the authors will retain all copyright and publishing rights.
</p>

<h2>The Prize</h2>
<p>
  The winning collaboration will receive $500 (to be split amongst the collaborators in the form of Amazon.com gift cards) and publication in the [TODO] issue of [TODO].
</p>

